activities:
1WorldSync, Inc. collects, uses and otherwise processes personal information received about individual contacts of former, current and prospective customers for the following purposes: 
•	Purchase and delivery of 1WorldSync products and services;
•	Customer support;
•	Technical support of 1WorldSync products and services;
•	Operating the 1WorldSync website and/or performing the associated business transactions;
•	Providing access to 1WorldSync websites, products or services;
•	Providing education on 1WorldSync products or services or related products or services; and
•	Performing marketing activities and otherwise communicating information regarding 1WorldSync products or services.
